<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Notes_for_Week_6:_2.3_The_Profit_Maximizing_Rule">Notes for Week 6: 2.3 The Profit Maximizing Rule</span></h2>
<h1> <span class="mw-headline" id="Marginal_Revenue">Marginal Revenue</span></h1>
<p><em>Marginal Revenue</em> is the change in total revenue from an additional unit sold.</p>
<p><em>Average Revenue</em> is the total revenue divided by the quantity sold.</p>
<p><em>Change in Profit</em> is the difference between Marginal Revenue minus Marginal Cost</p>
<table border="1">

